  "body": "# ðŸ’Ž Issue\r\n\r\n### Background\r\n\r\nIssue to track progress on peer scoring and rate limiting service implementation.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n- [x] Refactor \"bad responses counter\" into peer scoring system #6579\r\n- [x] `init-sync` slow peer (peers returning low number of blocks, constantly) descoring and throttling #6709\r\n- [x] `init-sync` weak peer (peers returning blocks that are not processable, low average slots advanced) handling #6709\r\n- [x] More sophisticated pruning #6701\r\n- [x] Peer scoring in p2p request/response layer #7480\r\n- [x] Inject peer scorer into Gossipsub v1.1 #6043\r\n- [ ] The feature has been gated by a flag in #8794 , once this is enabled by default in we can close this whole tracking issue. \r\n",
